name: Vancouver Community College
directions:
•	120A First floor, down the hall between the Interpreting and Advising offices, near the Culinary Arts kitchen
•	162B First floor, down the Fashion Arts hallways near the Community and Career Education department
•	219D Second floor, down the hallway to the left of the Administration office
•	339C Third floor, above the Student Union by the Dental department
•	435A Fourth floor, in the tower by Hospitality Management
